                                <span style="color:black;">Tiki Trading</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="side__product-name"><b>Apple iPhone 16 Pro Max - Titan Tự Nhiên - 512GB</b></div>
                            <div class="home__category-item__rating side__product-rating" style="margin-top:8px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <span style="border-left:1px solid; padding-left:5px; border-color:lightgray">
                                    Đã bán 95
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="home__category-item__price side__product-price">40.990.000<sup>₫</sup></div>
                            <div class="xemthem">Xem thêm</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="" style="text-decoration:none;">
                        <div style="text-align:center;" class="home__product-item side__product">
                            <div class="home__product-item__img" style=" border-radius: 0; background-image: url(https://salt.tikicdn.com/cache/750x750/ts/product/f7/ea/dd/53765af30c1da20b27dc20629bb31c1d.jpg); "></div>
                            <div class="tiki-trading">
                                <img class="tiki-trading-img" src="https://vcdn.tikicdn.com/ts/seller/d1/3f/ae/13ce3d83ab6b6c5e77e6377ad61dc4a5.jpg" />
                                <span style="color:black;">Tiki Trading</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="side__product-name"><b>Apple iPhone 16 Pro - Titan Tự Nhiên - 128GB</b></div>
                            <div class="home__category-item__rating side__product-rating" style="margin-top:8px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
                                <i class="fas fa-star" style="color: rgb(255, 196, 0);transform: scale(0.8);"></i>
